at FRBs are of extra-terrestrial\norigin. Second, we urge astronomers to pursue observations and understanding of\nPerytons since they form (at least) a formidable foreground for the FRBs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Feb 2014 18:54:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Feb 2014 18:19:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 20 Oct 2014 15:48:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
